text: Christa Bäckman (born 1 August 1962) is a Swedish archer. Bäckman competed at the 1996 Summer Olympics.Christa BäckmanChrista BACKMAN ==References== Category:1962 births Category:Living people Category:Swedish archers Category:Olympians for Sweden Category:People from Vänersborg
